{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2283232, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "控制空调的app已经有了\n控制电灯不是靠app就行的", "timestamp": 1629012408, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283233, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "安卓手机应该都可以遥控空调吧，灯现有条件有些难", "timestamp": 1629012427, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283234, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "空调很多手机自身可以，电灯就很麻烦了", "timestamp": 1629012445, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283241, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "电灯本身没有接受信号的硬件", "timestamp": 1629012511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283245, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "电灯得加装物理装置，学校线路应该不会给你改，空调买个带红外的手机或者淘宝买个红外模块即可", "timestamp": 1629012561, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283250, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "直接买一套智能家居就解决的事", "timestamp": 1629012595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283253, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "空调可以通过红外线遥控，手机只要能发射红外线就能控制空调。\n目前宿舍电灯的开关是是物理断开的，合上开关才能通电，手机显然无法单独提供这种动力。不过目前有很多卖的开关都是“智能”的，通过电信号控制灯的开灭而不是物理断开，这种就能通过手机操控。", "timestamp": 1629012622, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283367, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那求推荐一个控制空调的app呀", "timestamp": 1629013733, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283400, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "控制电灯开关可以用~~棍子~~牵引线-滑轮系统，脑补了一下感觉还挺简单的", "timestamp": 1629013978, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283422, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": 2283367, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 手机带红外啥的就行了", "timestamp": 1629014085, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2283424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 438966, "reply_to": 2283367, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 华为智慧生活有", "timestamp": 1629014096, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 438966, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "文科生求问\n做一个可以在手机上控制宿舍电灯开关/空调开关的app，有多难？涉及什么技术？", "timestamp": 1629012324, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629014094, "url": "", "vote": {}}}